wikiforum-forum-name:
Used as tooltip for the image. Parameters:
* $1 - the forum name
{{Identical|Forum}}

wikiforum-topic-name:
Page title. Parameters:
* $1 - a thread name
{{Identical|Forum}}

wikiforum-pages:
Followed by pagination links, like [01] [02] etc. Parameters:
* $1 is page number, for PLURAL support
{{Identical|Page}}

wikiforum-error-no-rights:
Used as error message.

The title for this error is any one of the following:
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-edit}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-category}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-add}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-write}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-general}}

wikiforum-error-readonly:
Used as error message having any one of the following headings:
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-category}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-forum}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-thread}}

wikiforum-error-move-thread:
Unused at this time.

Used as heading of error message.
{{Related|Wikiforum-error}}

wikiforum-error-add:
Used as heading of any one of the following error messages:
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-bad-title}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-double-post}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-general}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-no-reply}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-no-rights}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-no-text-or-title}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-thread-closed}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-title-already-exists}}
{{Related|Wikiforum-error}}

wikiforum-error-edit:
Used as heading of any one of the following error messages:
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-no-rights}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-no-text-or-title}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikiforum-error-no-reply}}
{{Related|Wikiforum-error}}

logentry-forum-add-category:
Shown when the user $1 created a new category, $5.

{{logentry}}
Additional parameters:
* $4 - category URL
* $5 - category name
{{Related|Logentry-forum}}

logentry-forum-add-forum:
Shown when the user $1 created a new forum, $5.

{{logentry}}
Additional parameters:
* $4 - forum URL
* $5 - forum title
{{Related|Logentry-forum}}

logentry-forum-add-thread:
Shown when the user $1 created a new thread, $4.

{{logentry}}
Additional parameters:
* $4 - thread title
{{Related|Logentry-forum}}

logentry-forum-add-reply:
Shown when the user $1 replied on the thread $4.

{{logentry}}
Additional parameters:
* $4 - thread title
{{Related|Logentry-forum}}

